==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Incrassation
<hw>In`cras*sa"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>incrassation</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The act or process of thickening or making thick;
the process of becoming thick or thicker.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The state of being incrassated or made thick;
inspissation.</def> <rj><au>Sir T. Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Incrassative</ent>⟦br⟧
